        <img src="/Images/Autonomous Car.png" alt="">

      <div class="content">
        <h3>Autonomous Rover</h3>
        <p>
          Intelligent rover capable of autonomous navigation,
          obstacle detection and real-time monitoring.
        </p>

        <div class="tags">
          <span>ROS</span>
